title.es: I just sat down. Already regret it.
title.pt-BR: Cold food again. Right on schedule.

comment.en: Their simple motivations always make me question my own complex struggles.
comment.es: Su simpleza siempre me hace dudar de mis líos.
comment.pt-BR: A simplicidade deles me faz duvidar do meu drama.

title.en: Why do I even bother, the food's cold already.
title.pt-BR: Sitting down. For five seconds, maybe.

comment.en: It's humbling how much simpler animal instinct seems compared to my daily lesson plans.
comment.es: Qué simple el instinto animal. Y yo con mis lecciones...
comment.pt-BR: Que simplicidade animal... Meus planos, então.
